videos.description: Kerry Blackshear Jr. holds off the Florida State defense and waits for Nickeil Alexander-Walker to make his move and cut to the basket.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Blackshear shows patience, setting up Alexander-Walker for two) 2019/3/5

videos.headline: Blackshear shows patience, setting up Alexander-Walker for two

videos.description: Off the turnover, Terance Mann feeds the ball up to Phil Cofer who throws down the alley-oop as FSU closes the gap on Virginia Tech.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Cofer's oop closes the Seminoles' gap on the Hokies) 2019/3/5

videos.headline: Cofer's oop closes the Seminoles' gap on the Hokies

videos.description: FSU's Trent Forrest is fouled causing multiple players to fall to the hardwood and the two teams head to a timeout exchanging words.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Tensions rise between the Seminoles and Hokies) 2019/3/5

videos.headline: Tensions rise between the Seminoles and Hokies

videos.description: Ahmed Hill pulls up for a Virginia Tech 3-pointer to tie Florida State at 61-61 leaving just 13 seconds on the clock.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Hill's jumper ties it up, forces OT) 2019/3/5

videos.headline: Hill's jumper ties it up, forces OT
